main event: On September 25, 1968, a witness observed a peculiar, bright disc-shaped object in the sky over Santa Barbara, California.
interesting points: The object was bright silver in color and made no noise., The observation lasted for approximately 101 minutes., The object emitted no exhaust or contrail during the observation., The witness is considered reliable and has no history of UFO sightings., Several members of an investigation committee felt the object could be mistaken for birds or other known phenomena.
